<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/styles/style.css">
    <title>North India Tourism</title>
</head>
<body>
    <%- include('partials/navbar') %>
    <%- include('partials/header') %>
    <main>
        <h2>North India - Major Touristic Spots</h2>
        <p>Discover the most popular destinations in North India.</p>
        
        <section class="tourist-spots">
            <div class="spot">
                <img src="/images/Taj.jpg" alt="Taj Mahal">
                <h4>Taj Mahal</h4>
                <p>One of the Seven Wonders of the World, located in Agra.</p>
                <p><strong>Best Time to Visit:</strong> October to March</p>
                <p><strong>Key Attractions:</strong> Taj Mahal, Agra Fort, Fatehpur Sikri</p>
                <p><strong>Nearest Airport:</strong> Agra Airport</p>
                <p><strong>Nearest Railway Station:</strong> Agra Cantonment</p>
            </div>
            <div class="spot">
                <img src="/images/jai.jpeg" alt="Jaipur">
                <h4>Jaipur</h4>
                <p>The Pink City, famous for its palaces and forts.</p>
                <p><strong>Best Time to Visit:</strong> October to March</p>
                <p><strong>Key Attractions:</strong> Hawa Mahal, Amber Fort, City Palace</p>
                <p><strong>Nearest Airport:</strong> Jaipur International Airport</p>
                <p><strong>Nearest Railway Station:</strong> Jaipur Junction</p>
            </div>
            <div class="spot">
                <img src="/images/var.jpg" alt="Varanasi">
                <h4>Varanasi</h4>
                <p>One of the oldest cities in the world, known for its ghats and temples.</p>
                <p><strong>Best Time to Visit:</strong> October to March</p>
                <p><strong>Key Attractions:</strong> Kashi Vishwanath Temple, Dashashwamedh Ghat, Sarnath</p>
                <p><strong>Nearest Airport:</strong> Lal Bahadur Shastri Airport</p>
                <p><strong>Nearest Railway Station:</strong> Varanasi Junction</p>
            </div>
        </section>
    </main>
    <%- include('partials/footer') %>
</body>
</html>

